@startuml
title Sequence: Student Login
actor Student
participant "Browser / UI" as UI
participant "Django View / Controller" as View
participant "Auth System / DB" as Auth
participant "Student Dashboard" as Dashboard

Student -> UI: Enter credentials
UI -> View: POST /login (credentials)
View -> Auth: Verify credentials
Auth --> View: Success / Failure
alt success
    View --> UI: Redirect (200)
    UI -> Dashboard: Load dashboard
else failure
    View --> UI: Show error
end
@enduml
